<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ل و ز<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٤٦٤٩ - ل و ز]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>لوَّزَ يلوِّز، تلويزًا، فهو مُلوِّز، والمفعول مُلوَّز <span class="c2">(للمتعدِّي)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• لوَّز القُطْنُ:</span> بدت ثمرتُه.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• لوَّز التَّمْرَ ونحوَه:</span> حشاه باللَّوْز بعد نزع نواه.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>